  @{bg shine}Close All (Local)    @{bg shadow}@{fg shine}@{i}A @{ui}@{fg text}@{bg shine}2@{bg background}
  @{bg shine}Close All            @{bg shadow}@{fg shine}@{i}A @{ui}@{fg text}@{bg shine}!@{bg background}
             :


@{u}@{b}Close@{ub}@{uu}
  Closes the current window.

@{b}Menu Shortcut:@{ub}  <Right Amiga> 1


@{u}@{b}Close All (Local)@{ub}@{uu}
  Closes all (TTManager) windows on the current screen.

@{b}Menu Shortcut:@{ub}  <Right Amiga> 2


@{u}@{b}Close All@{ub}@{uu}
  Closes all (TTManager) windows on all screens.

@{b}Menu Shortcut:@{ub}  <Right Amiga> !


@{b}Note:@{ub}  If @{"Warnings" link MENU_WARN} are enabled, and the tooltypes have been modified, a
     confirmation requester will appear before the window is closed.
@endnode


@node MENU_ABOUT "TTManager Menus:  Project - About"
