@{u}@{b}RestoreDefaultDir@{ub}@{uu}
  Resets the path used by file requesters to the default path.


@{b}Usage:@{ub}
  SetDefaultDir [DEFAULT] [ASCII] [AREXX] [ALL]

    DEFAULT - Restore the default path.

    ASCII   - Restore the default ACSII path.

    AREXX   - Restore the default ARexx path.

    ALL     - Restore all paths to their defaults.


@{b}Results:@{ub}
rc     - Always 0 (OK).
result - Not used.
