    <filename> - The name of an icon/file to open.
                 Multilpe filenames may be supplied.
                 If no <filename> is given, a file requester will open.
                 Enclose <filename> in quotation marks if it contains spaces.


@{b}Results:@{ub}
rc     - 10 (ERROR) if <filename> couldn't be loaded.
result - Not used.
